    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is an investment-grade 2011 Porsche 911 Carrera S (997.2) in concours-ready condition. This example features the 3.8L DFI flat-six, delivering 385 hp through a crisp 6-speed manual gearbox with zero mechanical lash. The chassis is equipped with PASM and a factory-spec limited-slip differential, ensuring optimal lateral grip and turn-in precision. Every component, from the high-pressure fuel pump to the multi-link rear suspension bushings, remains in factory-fresh state. The paint depth is consistent across all panels, exhibiting no swirl marks, while the interior leather retains its original matte finish and structural integrity. A comprehensive service dossier accompanies the vehicle.",
